name: Tap Tap Fast - Absolutely challenging tap puzzles - Quickly play by finger tapping on falling numbers
name_original: Tap Tap Fast - Absolutely challenging tap puzzles - Quickly play by finger tapping on falling numbers
description:
Tap Tap Fast is full of fun and challenging game, Your aim is to tap on falling numbers. Easy? then give it a try and figure out how much score you can get. You will get 20 seconds to tap all falling numbers. Number will fall rapidly as time passes. You can socially share your high score with your friends and challenge them to beat your score.

Play it for free now!!!
